## 🔄 Compatibility Notes

### Cross-IDE Compatibility
- Core rules from AI_POLICY.md apply universally
- Cursor-specific adaptations DO NOT affect other IDEs
- Git-based workflow remains consistent
- Agent commands follow standard patterns

### Migration Between IDEs
- Context files are portable
- Agent role definitions consistent
- Pipeline sequences identical
- Safety rules universal

## 🚀 Cursor-Specific Commands

### Agent Management
- `@role ANALYST` - Switch to analysis mode
- `@role DEVELOPER` - Switch to development mode
- `@mode hybrid` - Enable smart routing
- `@summary` - View current context

### Workflow Commands
- `@save` - Request approval checkpoint
- `@approve` - Approve and commit
- `@reject` - Request revisions
- `@delegate <agent> <task>` - Reassign work

